column4: Call for loose prop. Found prop cone loose, tightened with socket wrench. Prop and saildrive otherwise secure.
Checked for presenece of propeller. Propeller not present. Twine found wrapped around prop shaft.
Safety bolt found broken off inside prop shaft
Installed 851983-SR Volvo Penta 120 Saildrive Split Ring Zinc Anode
Line found wrapped around prop shaft. Anode absent. Light damage to lower keel: lead is compressed on forward lower port corner. See video for details. No obstructions detected in thru-hulls.
